{"languageMap":{},"form":"<form autocomplete=\"off\" novalidate=\"novalidate\" class=\"or clearfix\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"MarkdownExamples\">\n<!--This form was created by transforming a OpenRosa-flavored (X)Form using an XSL stylesheet created by Enketo LLC.--><section class=\"form-logo\"> </section><h3 dir=\"auto\" id=\"form-title\">MarkdownExamples</h3><section class=\"or-group-data or-appearance-field-list \" name=\"/form/Page0\"><label class=\"question non-select \"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\"># &lt;span style=\"color:red\"&gt;Introduction&lt;/span&gt;</span><span lang=\"\" class=\"or-hint active\">Formatting can be used for labels and hints to change the presentation of ODK Collect,&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This example was created using XLSForms.These 14 examples show the effect of formatting in the **Label** and the syntax used is shown in the **Hint** . Both Markdown and or HTML have been used.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The formatting used on this page will be demonstrated in the following examples. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;**IMPORTANT** in the following examples a &lt;span style=\"color:red\"&gt;~&lt;/span&gt; symbol is placed before the actual Markdown syntax to stop it having effect; remove all of the &lt;span style=\"color:red\"&gt;~&lt;/span&gt; in the actual code!</span><input type=\"text\" name=\"/form/Page0/IntroNote\" data-type-xml=\"string\" readonly=\"readonly\"/></label>\n            </section><!--end of group --><section class=\"or-group-data or-appearance-field-list \" name=\"/form/P1\"><label class=\"question non-select \"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\"># Going Large</span><span lang=\"\" class=\"or-hint active\">&lt;span style=\"color:red\"&gt;~&lt;/span&gt;# Going Large</span><input type=\"text\" name=\"/form/P1/one\" data-type-xml=\"string\" readonly=\"readonly\"/></label>\n            </section><!--end of group --><section class=\"or-group-data or-appearance-field-list \" name=\"/form/P2\"><label class=\"question non-select \"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\">###### Going Small</span><span lang=\"\" class=\"or-hint active\">&lt;span style=\"color:red\"&gt;~&lt;/span&gt;###### Going Small&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;the number of hashes used reduces the size.</span><input type=\"text\" name=\"/form/P2/two\" data-type-xml=\"string\" readonly=\"readonly\"/></label>\n            </section><!--end of group --><section class=\"or-group-data or-appearance-field-list \" name=\"/form/P3\"><label class=\"question non-select \"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\">Going &lt;span style=\"color:red\"&gt;red&lt;/span&gt;</span><span lang=\"\" class=\"or-hint active\">&lt;br&gt;Going &lt;*span style=\"color:red\"&gt;red&lt;*/span&gt;</span><input type=\"text\" name=\"/form/P3/three\" data-type-xml=\"string\" readonly=\"readonly\"/></label>\n            </section><!--end of group --><section class=\"or-group-data or-appearance-field-list \" name=\"/form/P4\"><label class=\"question non-select \"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\">Going &lt;span style=\"color:green\"&gt;green&lt;/span&gt;</span><span lang=\"\" class=\"or-hint active\">&lt;br&gt;Going &lt;*span style=\"color:green\"&gt;green&lt;*/span&gt; &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;You can try this with other colours; most primary colours should work.</span><input type=\"text\" name=\"/form/P4/four\" data-type-xml=\"string\" readonly=\"readonly\"/></label>\n            </section><!--end of group --><section class=\"or-group-data \" name=\"/form/P5\"><fieldset class=\"question simple-select \"><fieldset><legend><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\">Formatting works on labels for Choices also.</span>\n                    </legend><div class=\"option-wrapper\"><label class=\"\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"/form/P5/five\" data-name=\"/form/P5/five\" value=\"yes\" data-type-xml=\"select1\"/><span lang=\"\" class=\"option-label active\">&lt;span style=\"color:green\"&gt;Yes&lt;/span&gt;</span></label><label class=\"\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"/form/P5/five\" data-name=\"/form/P5/five\" value=\"no\" data-type-xml=\"select1\"/><span lang=\"\" class=\"option-label active\">&lt;span style=\"color:red\"&gt;No&lt;/span&gt;</span></label></div></fieldset></fieldset>\n            </section><!--end of group --><section class=\"or-group-data \" name=\"/form/P6\"><label class=\"question non-select \"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\">&lt;span style=\"font-family:cursive\"&gt;Cursive text&lt;/span&gt;</span><span lang=\"\" class=\"or-hint active\">&lt;br&gt;&lt;*span style=\"font-family:cursive\"&gt;Cursive text&lt;*/span&gt;</span><input type=\"text\" name=\"/form/P6/six\" data-type-xml=\"string\" readonly=\"readonly\"/></label>\n            </section><!--end of group --><section class=\"or-group-data \" name=\"/form/P7\"><label class=\"question non-select \"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\"># &lt;span style=\"font-family:cursive\"&gt;Large cursive text&lt;/span&gt;</span><span lang=\"\" class=\"or-hint active\">&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=\"color:red\"&gt;~&lt;/span&gt;# &lt;*span style=\"font-family:cursive\"&gt;Large cursive text&lt;*/span&gt; &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;You can combine formatting; here Markdown for LARGE has been combined with HTML for CURSIVE.</span><input type=\"text\" name=\"/form/P7/seven\" data-type-xml=\"string\" readonly=\"readonly\"/></label>\n            </section><!--end of group --><section class=\"or-group-data \" name=\"/form/P8\"><label class=\"question non-select \"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\">New&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Lines</span><span lang=\"\" class=\"or-hint active\">&lt;br&gt;New&lt;*br&gt;&lt;*br&gt;Lines &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This formatting has been used in many of the preceeding examples already.</span><input type=\"text\" name=\"/form/P8/eight\" data-type-xml=\"string\" readonly=\"readonly\"/></label>\n            </section><!--end of group --><section class=\"or-group-data \" name=\"/form/P9\"><label class=\"question non-select \"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\">&lt;u&gt;Underline&lt;/u&gt; &lt;i&gt;Italic&lt;/i&gt;</span><span lang=\"\" class=\"or-hint active\">&lt;br&gt;&lt;*u&gt;Underline&lt;*/u&gt; &lt;*i&gt;Italic&lt;*/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Two HTML examples of some basic formatting.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Bold&lt;/b&gt; &lt;*b&gt;bold&lt;*/b&gt; also works, but not in question labels as they are already bold.</span><input type=\"text\" name=\"/form/P9/nine\" data-type-xml=\"string\" readonly=\"readonly\"/></label>\n            </section><!--end of group --><section class=\"or-group-data \" name=\"/form/P10\"><label class=\"question non-select \"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\">&lt;span style=\"font-family:monospace\"&gt;Using Monospace font&lt;/span&gt;</span><span lang=\"\" class=\"or-hint active\">&lt;br&gt;&lt;*span style=\"font-family:monospace\"&gt;Using Monospace font&lt;*/span&gt; &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This will work for fonts that are supported by your device, so use with care.</span><input type=\"text\" name=\"/form/P10/ten\" data-type-xml=\"string\" readonly=\"readonly\"/></label>\n            </section><!--end of group --><section class=\"or-group-data \" name=\"/form/P11\"><label class=\"question non-select \"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\">[clickable link](https://nafundi.com/blog/posts/customize-odk-forms-with-fonts-colors-sizes-and-links/)</span><span lang=\"\" class=\"or-hint active\">&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=\"color:red\"&gt;~&lt;/span&gt;[clickable link]&lt;span style=\"color:red\"&gt;~&lt;/span&gt;(https://nafundi.com/blog/posts/customize-odk-forms-with-fonts-colors-sizes-and-links/) &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;A lot of the examples shown here have been taken directly from the great resource provided by Nafundi, so it's only right that when demonstrating a clickable link, the link is back to their resource.</span><input type=\"text\" name=\"/form/P11/eleven\" data-type-xml=\"string\" readonly=\"readonly\"/></label>\n            </section><!--end of group --><section class=\"or-group-data \" name=\"/form/P13\"><label class=\"question non-select \"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\">..*Bullets&lt;br&gt;..*In a title?</span><span lang=\"\" class=\"or-hint active\">&lt;br&gt;..*Bullets&lt;*br&gt;..In a title?</span><input type=\"text\" name=\"/form/P13/thirteen\" data-type-xml=\"string\" readonly=\"readonly\"/></label>\n            </section><!--end of group --><section class=\"or-group-data \" name=\"/form/P14\"><label class=\"question non-select \"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\">&lt;span style=\"color:red\"&gt;P&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=\"color:green\"&gt;u&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=\"color:yellow\"&gt;tt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=\"color:blue\"&gt;ing&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=\"font-family:cursive\"&gt; IT &lt;/span&gt; *all* &lt;u&gt;&lt;br&gt; to&lt;span style=\"color:red\"&gt;get&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;span style=\"color:blue\"&gt;her&lt;/span&gt;</span><span lang=\"\" class=\"or-hint active\">&lt;br&gt;&lt;*span style=\"color:red\"&gt;P&lt;*/span&gt;&lt;*span style=\"color:green\"&gt;u&lt;*/span&gt;&lt;*span style=\"color:yellow\"&gt;tt&lt;*/span&gt;&lt;*span style=\"color:blue\"&gt;&lt;*i&gt;ing&lt;*/span&gt;&lt;*/i&gt; &lt;*span style=\"font-family:cursive\"&gt;IT&lt;*/span&gt;*all* &lt;*br&gt;&lt;*u&gt;to&lt;*span style=\"color:red\"&gt;get&lt;*/span&gt;&lt;*span style=\"color:ble\"&gt;&lt;*/u&gt;her&lt;*/span&gt; &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Too much?</span><input type=\"text\" name=\"/form/P14/fourteen\" data-type-xml=\"string\" readonly=\"readonly\"/></label>\n            </section><!--end of group --><section class=\"or-group-data \" name=\"/form/P15\"><label class=\"question non-select \"><span lang=\"\" class=\"question-label active\">Formatting in hints works also</span><span lang=\"\" class=\"or-hint active\"># &lt;span style=\"font-family:cursive\"&gt;As Shown &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=\"color:red